git clone https://github.com/dunglas/symfony-docker.git myapp
Copiar los ficheros docker-compose.debug.yml y dockerfile
cd myapp

SYMFONY_VERSION=5.4.* docker-compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.debug.yml -f docker-compose.override.yml build

docker-compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.debug.yml -f docker-compose.override.yml up

docker-compose down --remove-orphans

En vscode, launch.json

